member.remarks:
Sample request:

    POST / Device - Creating new (make sure that deviceTypeId you are entering exists)
    {
        "name":"Device 1",
        "deviceTypeId":1
    }

Sample request:

    POST / DeviceType - Creating new
    {
       "name": "Racunar",
       "features":[
       {
            "name": "Operativni sistem"       
       }
        ]
    }

    PUT / DeviceType - Updating existing (make sure that device type exist in db)
    {
        "id":1,
        "name": "Racunar2",
        "features": [
             {
               "id":1,
               "name":"OS"
            }
        ]
    }
